{"tid":2242827,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派反對政府修例批JR法官3變2 鄭若驊突返港現身立會","createTime":"2020-10-14T09:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T16:47:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"00e65cba2721889e6a4855bf0c0542eb5e23f9d0","tid":2242827,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:50:38.000Z","msg":"司法機構聲稱為加快處理民事案件，尤其免遣返聲請，向立法會提出《2019年成文法（雜項規定）條例草案》，建議修訂《高等法院條例》中上訴庭處理部份司法覆核許可程序，由一般3名法官改由2名法官便可處理。立法會新一個延任會期處理的正是有關法案，多名建制派議員發言時支持政府修例，認為可讓司法機構靈活調配人手處理其他案件；民主派議員則表明反對有關修訂，認為會影響普通法要求的最高公平標準。<br />\n<br />\n工黨張超雄指，大律師公會早前在立法會發言時曾指擔心有關修訂會影響普通法所要求的最高公平標準，他亦質疑有關做法並不是顧及法庭整體運作效率的最穩妥做法。張又指，香港現時批出免遣返聲請的個案都比其他先進國家低，認為今次修例並無必要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/2WBI2JMZEZAKFD43A4O5W3RNI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2F2WBI2JMZEZAKFD43A4O5W3RNI4%2F&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2txiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=9fba5579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2F2WBI2JMZEZAKFD43A4O5W3RNI4%2F&h=23ba35b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/2WBI2JMZEZAKFD43A4O5W3RNI4/</a>"},{"pid":"5f288ee0f27bab000657ccd0aa6238e1bcd3731e","tid":2242827,"uid":143499,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d7e5cbda79459c1e9b81dd2b17129f306889112","tid":2242827,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c584ce6c982a6605c94b63051d269c1c937061a","tid":2242827,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d7e5cbda79459c1e9b81dd2b17129f306889112","tid":2242827,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":